{"about_the_game":"<strong>Join us on A Little Golf Journey.</strong> <br><br><strong>Embark on your adventure</strong> and bring colour back to the world as you complete golfing challenges across multiple destinations. With over 100 holes split across 10 stunning courses, you\u2019ll be able to unlock secrets and discover mysteries along the way.<br><br>Who knows what awaits you on your journey.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1232150/extras/ColourReveal.gif?t=1733412430\" /><br><br><strong>Discoveries that go beyond.</strong> Begin your golfing journey and discover a friendship that takes you across serene locations, all the way to the moon.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1232150/extras/InTheHole.gif?t=1733412430\" /><br><br><strong>No Caddie required.</strong> Just you, the ball and the soothing zen soundtrack as your companion. Play a quick round or stay for a while and immerse yourself in beautiful destinations. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1232150/extras/Japan.gif?t=1733412430\" /><br><br><strong>Looking for a par-ticular challenge? </strong><br>A Little Golf Journey has an abundance of secrets - and collectables - waiting to be unlocked, but hold on to your golf clubs, you\u2019ll need to complete some challenges along the way.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1232150/extras/Tron.gif?t=1733412430\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the<strong> expansive world map</strong> with <strong>over 100 holes</strong>, set in 10 stunning destinations.<br></li><li>Bring colour back to the world by completing challenges.<br></li><li>Discover <strong>secret holes, off-path mysteries </strong>and <strong>collectables</strong>.<br></li><li>Original soundtrack.<br></li><li>Simple, approachable controls - <strong>Aim, pull and release</strong> to shoot the ball and find the best route to the next hole. <strong>Easy to learn</strong>, but hard to put(t) down. <br><br>Prepare to Tee-off for your next adventure!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1232150/extras/Secrets.gif?t=1733412430\" /></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bullseye","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/4db22fd8df5cc2d9d473539a89005346e5b0b277.jpg"},{"name":"Golfy McGolfFace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/7d3a49cc6df75b3c34d4a7f1611e413240a485a4.jpg"},{"name":"Make Me A Star","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/4704a171bdf85ae10c1c23e5c9e6ecc7909b5239.jpg"},{"name":"Starry Eyed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/9cf281223e56067884dc2f10275eab359b235875.jpg"},{"name":"Blue thing, I think I love you","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/284e0c9d0c31968e7ba4068d6208fc01d59ed3db.jpg"},{"name":"Incomplete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/2d911d8e4bcdbacc5f63c4a079a708ed31f1191e.jpg"},{"name":"Super Powered","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/7ee70213bfad76c733a061c29ad0ca444ce7f92f.jpg"},{"name":"It Belongs In A Museum","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/b9fbff5cd3acbd48ceb7b9a41c8ad85a1245dd8b.jpg"},{"name":"Threading The Needle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/904e6ebdeca7ccd724bc83fceb4c491c3f3c3d54.jpg"},{"name":"Maxigolf","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1232150/f73683580b68054c359f3